1. *Zamisliti* da se nešto dogodi (To imagine that something happens)
2. On je mogao *zamisliti* kako će to izgledati (He could imagine how it would look)
3. Ona je *zamislila* da će joj sve proći bez problema (She imagined that everything would go without a problem)
4. Ona nije mogla *zamisliti* da se ovo dogodilo (She couldn't imagine that this happened)
5. Možeš li *zamisliti* koliko se toga promenilo (Can you imagine how much has changed)